metadata.name: The Miamien #1
metadata.description:
'The  Miamien' was created in partnership with Prosecco Industries, utlizes cc0 direction from Grant Yun on his original work 'The Alien', and was stylized/coded by Transient Labs' Ben Strauss in spirit of Art Basel, Miami 2022.  

This piece serves as the first dynamic work of art for the Proof of Innovation (POI) series hosted by Transient Labs. 'The Miamien' mint was only available to those holding a POI key.
